short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Open your Github repository with 3rd party web IDEs

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Chrome extension that helps you open Github repositories in a different 3rd party IDES.
 When navigating to any github repository, you can click on the green code button and see new options:
- Open in Github Dev
- Open in Github1s
- Open in StackBlitz
- Open in CodeSandbox
